# ITERATION 3 — Reservations, Check-In, Occupancy & Anomaly Detection

## Scope
Build the complete reservation lifecycle: creation, the Reservation Drawer for quick check-in (manual confirmation + optional QR scan), 10-minute no-show auto-cancel, configurable temporary leave rules, session heartbeat tracking, and "Unverified Occupancy" anomaly flagging after 30 minutes without a heartbeat.

