# ITERATION 5 — Notification Center

## Scope
Build the in-app Notification Center: template-based messages for all system events, per-role preference settings, an Inbox table with read/unread/archive status, visible send/failure logs, and a local retry queue (up to 3 attempts).

## Deliverables

### 1. Data Model

**`notifications` full shape:**
```ts
interface Notification {
  id?: number;
  recipientId: number;         // user id
  templateKey: NotificationTemplate;
  templateData: Record<string, string>;
  renderedSubject: string;     // filled after first successful deliver()
  renderedBody: string;
  status: 'Pending' | 'Delivered' | 'Failed' | 'Archived';
  isRead: boolean;

